    "translation":{"eng":"If someone does not establish a relationship with Nityānanda Prabhu, his human birth is wasted. Such an animalistic person is very wicked. Not uttering the name of Nitāi with his lips, he drowns himself in the [so-called] happiness of the material world. What, then, can his education and pedigree do for him?"}},{
