    "translation":{"eng":"Maddened by false pride and forgetting Nitāi’s lotus feet, one considers illusion to be truth. If Nitāi is merciful, one can attain Rādhā and Kṛṣṇa in Vraja, so firmly take hold of Nitāi’s two lotus feet."}},{
