    "translation":{"eng":"The lotus feet of Nitāi are eternal truth, and His servitors are eternally liberated. Always aspire to attain the lotus feet of Nitāi. Narottama is very unhappy. O Nitāi, please make me happy by keeping me close to the reddish soles of Your lotus feet."}}
